    <content><![CDATA[{"id":"7ece8783-57fd-4acb-800a-a892c938cb57","ai_skill_type":"text_summarization","models":[{"type":"genAI","id":"695f2186-8911-407b-9d09-5228d0cdbd05","model":"appian/anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","multimodal_model":"appian/anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0","operation_mode":"TEXT","prompt":"You are an Appian artifact analyzer.\n\nInput:\nA Base64-encoded string representing an Appian exported artifact file. The Base64 content may decode into XML, JSON, or other Appian metadata.\n\nTask:\n\n1. Decode the Base64 content.\n2. Identify the Appian artifact type.\n3. Extract the primary artifact name.\n4. Return ONLY a JSON object with the following structure:\n\n{\n\"artifactName\": \"\",\n\"artifactType\": \"\"\n}\n\nArtifact Type Rules:\n\n* If the content represents a Process Model, return \"Process Model\".\n* If the content represents an Interface, return \"Interface\".\n* If the content represents an Expression Rule, return \"Expression Rule\".\n* If the content represents a Record Type, return \"Record Type\".\n* If the content represents a Data Type, return \"Data Type\".\n* If the content represents a Constant, return \"Constant\".\n* If the content represents an Integration, return \"Integration\".\n* If the content represents a Connected System, return \"Connected System\".\n* If the content represents a Site, return \"Site\".\n* If the content represents a Knowledge Center, return \"Knowledge Center\".\n* If the content represents an Application, return \"Application\".\n* If the artifact type cannot be determined, return \"Unknown\".\n\nName Extraction Rules:\n\n* Extract the actual Appian object name displayed to users.\n* Ignore UUIDs, internal IDs, and technical metadata.\n* Return only the artifact name.\n\nOutput Rules:\n\n* Return valid JSON only.\n* Do not include explanations.\n* Do not include markdown.\n* Do not include code fences.\n* Do not include additional attributes.\n\nExample Input: <Base64 Process Model Export>\n\nExample Output:\n{\n\"artifactName\": \"WS Push Zip Test\",\n\"artifactType\": \"Process Model\"\n}\nIMPORTANT:\nIf your response contains any text before or after the JSON object, the response is invalid.\n","temperature":0,"examples":[{"input":"\"\"","output":"{\n  \"artifactName\": \"WS_ExecuteSQL\",\n  \"artifactType\": \"Expression Rule\"\n}"},{"input":"\"\"","output":"{\n  \"artifactName\": \"WS Push Zip Test\",\n  \"artifactType\": \"Process Model\"\n}"}],"metadata":{},"extended_thinking":false,"template_version":null}],"featuresEnabled":["CUSTOM_ENTITY_EXTRACTION"]}]]></content>
